Sleek
column13: smooth and sophisticated
column14: this wonderfully designed analog watch from Sonata\u2019s Yuva Gold collection for women comes well equipped to accurately keep track of time and do so with great style. Presenting a prominent design that is all about expressing grace and elegance
column15:
this women’s watch is a definite choice for any of your casual get-togethers.

Body and Design

The Sonata Yuva Gold Analog Watch sports a contemporary dial that houses an attractively coloured watch face. The dial’s background has a subtle pattern so as to eliminate any sense of monotony. As part of the distinctive design
column16: the dial on this women\u2019s analog watch features only six hour markers which are on the 3
column17: 4 and 5-hour positions on the right and the 9
column18: 10 and 11-hour positions on the left side of the dial. These hour markers along with the watch\u2019s three time indicating hands have a sophisticated metallic finish
column19:
which against the deep colour of the watch face provides for easy and trouble-free time reading.

The stylish and contemporary dial on this Sonata Yuva Gold watch is enveloped in a sturdy case with the same metallic finish as the watch hands and the hour markers. This case not only adds to the watch’s high aesthetic value but also provides the all-important dial with a much needed level of durability and protection.

Functions and Other Features

All the changes and adjustments that you wish to make to the positions of the watch hands can easily be accomplished with the rotating crown located on the right side of the dial’s case. This metallic case has extensions at the top and bottom portions forming lugs that serve the purpose of attaching it to the watch’s extremely attractive leather strap. The leather strap helps keep this Yuva Gold analog watch from Sonata comfortably attached to your wrist as long as your need. The dial’s sturdy case combines with a hardy clear glass cover to give the watch the ability to be water-resistant up to a depth of 30 m.

Boasting a high level of aesthetics

The Sonata watch has a softly coloured round dial that is dotted with elegant time markers and three display hands. The time markers also have been set to resemble how the ripples begin to amplify. The dial is held in the beautiful metallic case that gleams like the morning dew. The case has a metallic finish that makes the watch look stunning on your wrist. The uniquely shaped lugs of the watch serve the dual purpose of being decorative and of holding the case on the sleek leather strap. The watch sits firmly on your wrist thanks to the secure buckle clasp.

Functions and Other Features

The Sonata watch isn’t merely an accessory that can be paired with your clothes
column16: it is a timekeeper that ticks steadfastly by your side all day
column17: everyday. Along with strength and durability
column18:
the watch delivers water resistance up to a depth 30 m which means the watch is splash and rain resistant. When you get caught in the rain you can step out with confidence and enjoy nature\u2019s most formidable blessing and not have to worry about the watch dying on you.

\r\n

\r\n\tThis watch has been built for the free spirited woman. A wonderful pick from the Sonata Yuva Gold series
column19: the watch captures the beauty of nature and has encapsulated it in the body of this elegant watch. For the woman who believes that true beauty rests in the soul
column20:
Sonata Yuva Gold Analog Watch is an excellent match.

\n

column15:
this watch from Sonata can be worn with all your casual wear to college or work. Team this trendy watch with your fashionable kurtis and stylish T-shirts and make an enormous style statement wherever you go.

Body and Design

The watch has a youthful and vibrant design that is sure to make you stand out in a crowded party where you are in a room full of people. The watch is built around an impressively crafted round dial which gives the watch a graceful and refined finish. Plain and simple

column17: minutes and hour hand are provided with a rich metallic finish
column18:
while the digits on the watch are furnished with deep contrasting colours against the light background of the watch. Use of bright and vivid colours enhances the watch’s aesthetic value and gives it a classy look and feel. The highly attractive dial of the watch is steadfastly and comfortably fitted to your wrist at all times with the help of a stylish leather strap that is extremely durable.

Functions and Other Features

Apart from the watch’s appealing femininity and lavish design
column19: the watch also provides you with accurate and reliable time reading. This watch from Sonata is water resistant up to a depth of 30 m and is hence
column20: well-protected from accidental spills

'desc': [u'

Sonata Yuva Analog Watch - For Women (Pink) Price: Rs.765

Key Features

  • Round Dial
  • Pink Strap
  • Water Resistant

If a man calls you girly for liking pretty pink clothes
column13: fluffy teddys and chocolates
column14: you should take it as a compliment. To celebrate everything that is delicate and every so endearing about women Sonata presents a lovely analog watch\xa0from the Yuva Series that resonates with feminine charm. This elegant watch is for the woman who is unabashed by her femininity and does not pretend to be a gearhead to please others. Her innocence is her greatest asset and the Sonata Yuva watch\xa0is an accessory that matches her personality and her wardrobe. The Sonata Yuva watch goes well with your casual kurtis
column15:
jeans and even your pretty summer dresses. So dress up all you want and feel prettier than ever because you deserve it.\xa0

Body and Design

The soft toned round dial is beautified with slim time markers in Roman numerals. The bezel and case of the watch have been studded with clear stones only to harp on the old saying that diamonds are a girl’s best friends and rightfully so. The stones have been carefully placed to give the give the watch depth
column16:
but without overdoing it. To hold the lovely timepiece elegantly on your wrist is a leather strap with tonal stitching. The leather strap is soft on your skin and makes the watch comfortable to wear all day.

Functions and Other Features

If there is one scene from Bollywood movies that every girl indisputably loves it’s when the heroine runs out into the rain to do that splendid rain dance. You can go ahead do your own version of the rain dance on the spur of a moment and nothing can hold you back from it
column17:
not even your pretty watch because the Yuva watch is water resistant up to 30 m making it splash-and rain-resistant.

The Sonata Yuva Analog watch is the true essence of femininity and gives you a beautiful accessory to pair with your clothes. You don’t have to play videogames or drive fast cars to be noticed because all you need is the charming innocence that makes you beautiful and the Sonata Yuva Analog Watch adds to your innate beauty.

column3: 'title': [u'\n                    Sonata Bracelet Analog Watch  - For Women            ']
column12:
'desc': [u'

Sonata Bracelet Analog Watch - For Women (Gold) Price: Rs.1315

Key Features

  • Oval Dial
  • Golden Strap
  • Water Resistant

Slim
column13: sleek and sophisticated
column14: this wonderfully designed watch is from Sonata. An analog watch from the Bracelet collection for women
column15:
this chic timepiece comes well equipped to accurately keep track of time and also do so with great elegance and style. This is an ideal accessory to sport on dressy occasions; the graceful timepiece will blend in with any attire that you have stacked up in your wardrobe over time. Wear this watch to a party and mesmerise other guests with the infallible charm of this graceful time wear.

Body & Design

The ultra-chic design that this Sonata analog wristwatch is built around finds its origin at the watch’s impressively crafted oval shaped dial
column16: which sports a very plain and uncluttered light coloured background. The seconds and the hour hand are given a rich metallic finish
column17:
while the minutes hand and most of the digit markers are given a rich contrasting colour against the light background. This clever use of colours not only enhances the aesthetic value of the watch but also makes it extremely easy to tell the time with just a simple glance at the dial.

The Sonata Bracelet watch for women is kept firmly and comfortably attached to your wrist at all times with the help of a plush metal strap which also carries the same colour as the dial’s digit markings and the watch hands. The unique shape of the strap adds a glamorous touch to this fashionable time wear. The comfy strap will make sure that you do not feel discomfited even after prolonged use of the chic timepiece.

Functions and Other Features

Monsoon always arrives unannounced. A few spells of unanticipated shower can leave you drenched to the core. However

  • Pink Strap

column13:

    • Life would be a sad old picture if we didn’t add a little colour to it and the Q&Q Analog watch has been designed to brighten up your day with a splash of colour. This vibrant sports watch is for the woman who is upbeat and takes life in her stride. The watch can go with your denim skirts and T-shirts and would even look stunning when you wear a suit and trousers.

    The colourful Q&Q analog watch not only adds spunk to your style but also proves to be a resilient watch that is meant to back the tough cookie that you are. Whether you enjoy basketball on weekends or want to sit back and sip coffee with friends
column14:
the watch adds to your style and stays put when you are out on your daily adventures. The impeccable precision of the quartz mechanism ensures that the watch is running in time and so are you.

Body and Design

The striking round dial is flanked with bold time markers and 3 equally stunning time display hands. On the bezel of the watch you will find clear 10-second markers in numerals. The watch comes together with the bright and vibrant plastic strap. The use of plastic makes the watch durable and resistant to wear and tear. The plastic strap is comfortable on the skin and allows you to wear the watch for long periods of time.

Functions and Other Features

If you are someone who likes helping your mom out in their garden and don’t mind digging your hands into the dirt then the Q&Q watch is just right for you. The watch is protected with a mineral glass dial cover that keeps the watch safe from scratches. And even if you get a little dirt on the watch you can simply give it a thorough wash because the watch is water resistant up to a depth of 50 m. The plastic strap doesn’t get wet and can simply be wiped down to clean it.

Once you are done helping mom out you can head straight out to meet your friends at the beach. The snazzy sports watch is sure to match your ever so awesome swim wear so
column15: whether you choose to play volleyball on the beach or take a swim in sea
column16:
you look great with this dapper accessory. The Q&Q also features the very handy date display so you don’t have to fumble about with your phone to know what the date is.

This youthful watch from Q&Q is for the woman who is active and adventurous and needs a watch that can keep up with her busy and bustling life.

'desc': [u'

Maxima Analog Watch - For Women (White) Price: Rs.845

Key Features

  • Rectangular Dial
  • White Strap
  • Water Resistant
  • Buckle Clasp

Watches are the perfect way to complement the clothes you wear. Are you looking for a simple and elegant watch that can stand up to the demands of daily use
column13: yet be stylish enough to wear on those classy evenings out? Perhaps
column14: you think of a watch as an accessory and aim to add a few more to that collection of yours. Whatever the need may be
column15:
the Maxima analog watch for women seems to be the appropriate choice. This casual watch from Maxima sports a classy analog dial driven by a battery powered quartz mechanism that keeps both you and the watch ticking right through the day.\xa0

Body and Design

The analog watch from Maxima comes with a leather strap. The leather strap makes this watch very comfortable to wear over long periods of time. The watch also features a rectangular dial that is encased in a steel bezel. The simplistic design of the rectangular dial
column16: with its three display hands
column17:
really accentuates the beauty of such a watch.

Functions and Other Features

\r\n

\r\n\tThe women\'s analog watch from Maxima is designed to be water resistant as well as water resistant to a depth of 30 m
column18:
making your next trip to one of those scenic waterfalls even more enjoyable.

\xa0

column12:
'desc': [u'

Maxima Ssteele Analog Watch - For Women (Silver) Price: Rs.1485

Key Features

  • Oval Dial
  • Silver Strap
  • Water Resistant

Break away from the prevalent fashion trends and set new standards of glamour with your style quotient. Let the Maxima Ssteele series become the beacon of your identity and represent your individuality through its unique craftsmanship. Flaunt this exquisite Maxima Ssteele Analog Watch for women with \xe9lan and enjoy the expression of awe in the eyes of others for your timepiece. The stylish time wear for women blends in effortlessly with any attire
column13: transforming you into a diva. A perfect accessory for any occasion
column14:
the dainty timepiece can be worn for your colleague\u2019s house warming party as well as the wedding of a friend.

Body and Design

\r\n\tCrafted with minute attention to detail
column15: the women\u2019s watch from Maxima lets you bask in the glory of wearing an elegant and sophisticated timepiece. The charming time wear comes with an oval dial
column16: which wears a look of serenity. Flaunting a dark-coloured background
column17: the dial of the stylish timepiece sports a sophisticated look. Moreover
column18: the representation of the hour markers with glittering crystals adds to the glamour of the Maxima ladies\u2019 watch. The prominent watch hands ease the process of reading time
column19:
apart from adding to the enigmatic sheen of the timepiece.

\r\n\tThe wonderful design of the dial is complemented by the polished appearance of the watch case. Moreover
column20: the Maxima watch is equipped with a stainless steel strap that ensures a comfortable experience for the wearer. No matter how long you keep the watch strapped on
column21: you will not feel an iota of discomfort
column22: thanks to the bracelet-type strap. Stainless steel is known to be a durable metal alloy that is resistant to corrosion. So
column23:
you can shed all your worries about the longevity of your prized time wear.

Functions and Other Features

\r\n\tAlong with its exquisite physical attributes
column24: the trendy watch also excels in the function of timekeeping. Thanks to its water-resistance capacity
column25: the Maxima watch qualifies as the ideal accessory during the monsoon. Able to withstand splashes of water
column26: the timepiece can be worn even as you spend some lazy moments in your apartment\u2019s swimming pool after work. The Maxima Ssteele analog watch is an ideal accessory for women who love to sport a glamorous look
